Those in the know believe the new Bafana Bafana coach Hugo Broos could be the answer to the ailing national team. eNCA reporter, Tshepo Thobane, reports.Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Those in the know believe the new Bafana Bafana coach Hugo Broos could be the answer to the ailing national team. Broos comes into the job with a lot of pressure on him and becomes the latest in a long line of coaches, expected to revive the fortunes of Bafana Bafana. Qualifying for the FIFA World Cup in Qatar next year is his immediate challenge. READ: Hugo Broos appointed new Bafana Bafana coach There's no doubt 69-year-old Hugo Broos is facing a daunting task as Bafana Bafana coach. He comes into a national side that has long underperformed and recently failing to qualify for next year’s AFCON tournament Broos is expected in the country sometime next week.